Prabhakar Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Prabhakar is recorded 2,953 times globally, ranking it as the 15,218th most common name worldwide.

Prabhakar is most prevalent in India, with 1,080 occurrences, making it the 698th most popular name in the country.
